Argued and submitted September 19, Mary Darlene STEVENS, Respondent, v. Dennis MARNEY and Pamela Marney, Appellants. (90-81332; CA A68641) 820 P2d 905 Kathleen G. Dolan, Eugene, argued the cause for appellants. With her on the brief was Lane County Legal Aid Service, Inc., Eugene. PER CURIAM

remanded for award of attorney fees; otherwise affirmed November 13, 1991

No appearance for respondent.

Before Richardson, Presiding Judge, and Joseph, Chief Judge, and Deits, Judge.
